column2: SELECT u.up_name as [name], # + cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + #+ cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + # as objID, p.ra, p.dec, dbo.fPhotoTypeN (p.type) as type, p.c = modelMag_u, p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMag_z, p.modelMagErr_z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID ORDER BY x.up_id
